signatures.note:
Quire marks are written in the upper margin of the following leaves:
3r: ፩ “1”;
12r: ፪ “2”; 
21r: ፫ “3”; 
29r: ፬ “4”;
37r: ፭ “5”;
44r: ፮ “6”;
52r: ፯ “7”.

handDesc.handNote:
                        Careful.
                        Black; red.
                        Gabra KrǝstosThe concluding supplication formula (54ra) mentions ʾabuna Gabra Krǝstos as the scribe (different from the scribe of QSM-023 and FBM-001).19th century


